Get Insights into Deal Pricing with the Pricing Analytics App

Create an app to get instant insights into how your organization prices deals. Connect with Einstein Discovery to get discount recommendations for every quote.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition. Requires a CRM Analytics and Salesforce CPQ license. To create the app, you also need the Einstein Discovery license.

USER PERMISSIONS
NEEDED
To create and manage the Pricing Analytics app: Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps AND Manage Einstein Discovery
To use the Pricing Analytics app: Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps

Create the Pricing Analytics App

Before you create the app, make sure that:

Your org has at least one Salesforce CPQ Quote Line record.
The Analytics Integration User has the appropriate Salesforce field-level security to view the fields that you want to analyze.

Create and select the Pricing Analytics template to open the guided flow. Name and save your app.

Use the Pricing Analytics App

Deploy the Einstein Discovery model. Use bulk scoring to write back recommended discounts to the Salesforce Quote Line object. Run the dataflow.
